snippet.textDisplay:
O mustafa ( the chosen one) , o mujtaba ( the one selected amongst many), Show us mercy...
 O hand of mercy to the helpless and hopeless, I am sinner, feeble and helpless and You are my only refuge. 
O musk willow, scattering fragrance, 
 O sweet breeze of the early morn
 O you who cures ills, O you with the breath of Jesus
 O consoler of the grief-stricken
 O auspicious messenger
 I beg you in the name of that same fragrance
 O morning breeze, if you go
 To that sacred land someday
 Present my greetings at the blessed grave
 Where the revered Prophet rests.....


the melody and the beautiful poetic lyrics inarabic evokes imaan tauhid and ishq for that Ultimate Truth... even when you are not a believer... Such devotions always bear fruits  in your heart... brings the ibaadat closer to Him... We become fanaa ul fanaaa in His Divine presence in the whole of cosmos... too beautiful is the feeling to be uttered in tongue
